Package: cartovl
Title: An R Interface to 'carto-vl'
Version: 0.4.0
Date: 2019-09-17
Authors@R: person("Stefan", "Kuethe", email = "crazycapivara@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Stefan Kuethe <crazycapivara@gmail.com>
Description: Makes 'carto-vl' <https://carto.com/developers/carto-vl/>, an open source JavaScript library
  to create vector-based visualizations on top of mapbox-gl <https://docs.mapbox.com/mapbox-gl-js/api/>,
  available within R via the 'htmlwidgets' package.
URL: https://github.com/crazycapivara/cartovl/
BugReports: https://github.com/crazycapivara/cartovl/issues/
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports:
  htmlwidgets,
  magrittr,
  geojsonsf
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
